    "description": "<p>Established in 2003, BHCC Construction Pte Ltd is a home-grown building construction company focusing on the institutional, industrial, commercial and residential projects. From a humble beginning, the company has established its credentials as a reputable contractor, nurturing from strength to strength to formulate a team of administrative and technical staffs, capable in its respective field of construction expertise and construction support service capabilities.</p>\n\n<p>Our relentless pursuit of construction excellence brings us the notable reputation. Through the years, BHCC has developed rapidly from a specialist of reinforcement concrete works to an A1 grade contractor in General Building and has proven its ability to successfully and competently execute the many projects to completion. Our achievements includes GGB Excellence, Bizsafe Partner, SHARP Awards etc..</p>\n",
